com.intel.device.api.voice

Interface VoiceController

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AsyncVoiceController, FightClubVoiceController, PhoneVoiceController

    public interface VoiceController
    Provides audio management for an Audio Enabled Device. Its methods perform tasks such as streaming, listening for audio input and transforming audio data between the wearable device and the application.
